1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,399
Take a moment now to reflect.

2
00:00:02,399 --> 00:00:08,800
Think about a recent interaction at work — with a patient, a colleague, or a visitor.

3
00:00:08,800 --> 00:00:13,200
Was there a moment where accessibility could have been handled differently?

4
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:16,000
Not necessarily a failure, but an opportunity.

5
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:22,000
On screen, you will see a text box where you can write a brief reflection.

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:30,000
You might consider questions like: What barriers have I noticed in my workspace that I had not thought about before?

7
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:35,600
When was the last time I asked someone how they preferred to receive information?

8
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:39,200
What is one thing I could change this week?

9
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:40,800
Your reflection is private.

10
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:44,800
It is not shared with your manager or anyone else.

11
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:47,200
This is for your own learning.

12
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:50,000
Take as much time as you need.

13
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,399
When you are ready, move on to the action planning screen.
